    "Trigger for Escalation Based on EmotionSometimes the way people express themselves matters more than the substance of their words.",
    "Large language models designed using prompt-engineering may identify emotional cues.",
    "The model may begin an escalation route when a message shows annoyance or urgency, like, \"This is the third occurrence, I am quite disappointed.\"",
    "A prompt may ask the model to evaluate more sentiment, context, and previous interactions to decide if the issue should be given top priority or escalated to a human agent.",
    "It's AI combined with empathy."
